query:
SELECT 
  i.productId,
  i.locationId,
  i.tenantId,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as available,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.code as zoneCode,
  p.sku as productSku,
  p.description
FROM inventory i
INNER JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON i.locationId = wl.id
INNER JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wl.zoneId = wz.id
INNER JOIN products p ON i.productId = p.id
WHERE p.sku = '443060' AND wl.code = 'H01-01-01';
